[[File:Scissors.jpg|right|frame|Miyayaliwang gunting - para king papil, kusina, ampong pamanayi]]
Deng '''gunting''' (‘’scissors’’ king Inglis) [[kasangkapan]] lang magagamit king pamangupit king maimpis a materialis a mangailangan mung ditak a [[puersa]] o sikanan.

Gagamitan la reti king pamamutut, alimbawa, king [[papil]], [[kartun]], [[palara]], maimpis a [[plastic]], pamangan, [[tela]], [[lubid]], ampong [[kawad]]. Maliari la muring gamitan king pamanurud king [[buak]] deng gunting. 

E anti king [[kutsiliu]], ing metung a paris a gunting, bibilugan de reng aduang taram a maki piesang dudurutan (pivot). E la makaing mataram deng keraklan kareng gunting; itang puersa ning [[Shearing (physics)|pamangupit]] pilatan da reng aduang taram yapin ya ing mangupit. Lalu lang e mataram deng gunting da reng ának, at keraklan makakambil (maki proteksiun) lang plastic deng taram. 

== Pamangalo (Mechanics) ==
[[File:Schere Gr 99.jpg|left|100px]]
Agpang kareng pamagaral king pamangalo (mechanics), maliari lang ituring primera clasi at dobling [[baluat]] (double-lever]], nung nu magsilbi yang [[fulcrum]] ing pivot (pidudurutan). Ba yang pututan ing materialis a makapal o mabayat, maliari yang samantalanan ing [[w:mechanical advantage|mechanical advantage]] ning baluat kapamilatan ning pamaglapit (anggang maliari) ning materialis ketang fulcrum. Alimbawa, nung itang puersang gagamitan (alimbawa, king gamat) dobli ya dáyu king fulcrum kesa ketang lugal nung nu ating pupututan (alimbawa, kapirasung papil), dobli ya ing puersa ketang lugal a pipupututan kesa ketang puersang magagamit kareng talanan. 
Sasamantalanan da reng espesial a gunting, alimbawa deng [[bolt cutters]], ing leverage o puestu, kapamilatan ning makabang talanan, dapot malapit ya king fulcrum ing materialis a gupitan. Makagupit la reng gunting kapamilatan ning pamangamit king puersang [[w:shear stress]] king lugal a pipupututan, a sobra king tibe o kuniat ([[shear strength]]) ning materialis.

== Amlat ==
[[File:Scissors_turkey.jpg|thumb|right|Deng gunting ibat king [[w:2nd Century|kaduang siglu]], [[Turkey]]]]
Ukulan dang meimbentu la reng gunting libu dinalan a banua bayu i Cristo (1500 BC) king [[w:Egypt|Ehiptu]] .<ref>http://inventors.about.com/library/inventors/blscissors.htm </ref> Mapaliaring [[w:shears|shears]] la reti nung nu makabili ya ing pidudurutan banda king sepu sumangid ning talanan .<ref>http://www.everything2.com/index.pl?node=scissors</ref> Inimbentu do reng Romanu deng cross-bladed scissors (gunting a mikukurus taram) manga dinalan a banua aniang panaun nang Cristo (AD 100). 

Mika maragul a takbang king paniulung da reng gunting aniang 1761, aniang gewa nong [[Robert Hinchliffe]] deng mumunang gunting a gawa king bakal a pundidung pepakintab (polished cast steel). Mebie ya king [[Cheney Square]], [[London]], at sasabian dang ya ing mumunang taung migpalual karatulang mibulalag king sarili na antimong "fine scissor manufacturer".(gagawa king masanting diling uring gunting) ".
