== Deng gunting a pangkusina ==
[[File:kitchenscissors.jpg|thumb|left|Gunting a pangkusina]]
Ausan da la muring ''kitchen shears'' deng gunting a pangkusina o ''kitchen scissors''. Ing pekamaulagang pamiyaliwa yapin ing lugal ning fulcrum. Mas malaut ya kareng talanan ing fulcrum kareng gunting a pangkusina bang mas maragul ing leverage, at mas masikan ing puersa bang makagupit. Malagua la mung makagupit kareng mangalati nang butul ning [[manuk]] deng matas a uring gunting a pangkusina.{{Fact|date=February 2008}}

== Deng gunting a pangkaliweti ==
[[File:2scissors-clean.jpg|thumb|left|200px|Deng gunting a pang-kaliweti (kaili) ampong pang-wanan (wanan)]]
Keraklan, pekabage lang gamitan king wanan a gamat deng gunting, dapot atin nang gunting a ''pang-kaliweti'' (left-handed) para king kailing gamat. Mas mayan lang gamitan king gamat a kaili deng gunting a pang-kaliweti. Uling lalagpus la king metung at metung deng taram ning gunting, e la saktung mibabalansi (symmetric) deti. Agiang kapilan, tutu iting e pangabalansi nu la man makaturu at nanu la man tabas deng talanan: pane mung pareu ing pamikurus ning taram king babo. E la murin balansi deng gamat da reng tau, at neng sasara ya iti, e la patikdong magsara deng tindaragul ampong taliri, nun e atin yang parting pa-kera o pa-gilid ing pamangimut da reti. Nung talnan no ning wanan a gamat deng gunting a pang-wanan, mas malapit ya king katawan ing taram ning tindaragul, ania ing pamilapit da reng aduang taram a pangupit ing natural nang kimut ning wanan a gamat. Lindas (kontra) kaniti, natural naman king kailing gamat ing pikawani la reng taram a pangupit. Karagdagan kaniti, nung talnan no ning wanan a gamat deng gunting a pang-wanan, makalto ya ing gilid a mataram (a pangupit), dapot nung king kaili yang gamat gamitan iti, atyu king gulut ning taram a makababo ing gilid nang mataram ning gunting, at e makalto itang gugupitan. 

.Ating lang pamisaling gunting a ausan dang [[w:ambidextrous|ambidextrous]], o para king sanu mang gamat. Makabalansi la reng karelang talanan, ania alang yang pamialiwa ing talanan ning tindaragul ampo ing karing taliri, at mangasikan la pivot (pirinan torniliu), ania kabud na la mu dudurut deng taram, at e la kikimut pa-gilid. Nanupata, pang-wanan la pa murin deng keraklan kareng gunting a "ambidextrous". Agiang makaputut lang masalese deti, e ne akit ning taung kaliweti ing taram a mángupit. Maliaring mika tutung gunting a "ambidextrous" nung dobli ing gilid dang matalas deng taram, at nung maliari yang idurut a alus todu ing gulut ning taram, ba yang maging bayung gilid a pangupit. [http://www.sinistershop.com/c_scissors.htm]. Atin nang patent ({{US patent|3978584}}) a mipagkalub kareng tuneng ambidextrous a gunting.    

Magkasákit lang gumamit kareng gunting a para king e ustung gamat deng keraklan kareng tau, agiang kareng kaliweting misane nang gagamit kareng gunting a pang-wanan, taganang mas malaguang paintunan. Kailangan dong paka-puersan deng taram ba rong apamutut deti, at mánikal la batal king pangadukuang o pangagaung ba rang akit ing karelang pupututan. Maliari muring maglakuan bakas king gamat, sugat, at king lambatan, [[kaliu]], ining e natural a pamangimut.

== Deng espesial a gunting ==
[[File:Scissors_china.jpg|thumb|280px|Gunting a megawa king [[China]] kanitang panaun ning [[w:Tang dynasty|Tang dynasty]] ([[618]]-[[907]] AD)]]
Ating mapilang espesial a uri da reng gunting a maki miyayaliwang gamit. Deni reng mapilan kareti.

*Deng [[pinking shears]] gunting la nung nu maki ipan ya ing taram at gagamitan la king pamangupit tela, ba yang e matatastas ing tela.
*Deng [[tin snip]] gunting lang gagamitan king pamamutut king [[sheet metal]] anti ing tin plate, o [[yeru]]ng para king bubungan.
*Deng [[pruning shear]], [[secateur]] ampong [[lopper]] gunting lang gagamitan king mula para king pamamutut kareng [[pun dutung]] (trees) ampong [[palungpung]] (shrubs).
*Deng [[trauma shears]], o "tuff cut", are gunting lang mangasanting a gagamitan kareng e asahan (emergency) a pamag-responding medikal ampong pamanyagip.
* Deng trimming scissors magagamit la ba yang gawang maimpis ing makapal a buak ba yang e masiadung maglupang malabung iti
* Deng grass shears gagamitan la king pamamutut king [[dikut]].
* Deng jaws of Life (lon ya ing [[w:hydraulic rescue tools]]) gagamitan la king pamangupit king makapal a sheet metal keng pamaniagip tau
* Deng [[w:throatless shear]]s gagamitan la king pamangupit kareng komplikadung tabas king sheet metal
* Deng [[w:Sheep_shearing#Shearing_devices|wool shears]] gagamitan la king pamangupit lana (wool) ibat king buak da reng animal
* Deng [[poultry shears]] gagamitan la king pamamutut kareng [[ayup]].
* Deng [[hair shears]] - gagamitan la king pamangupit buak deng [[w:Cosmetology|cosmetologist]] o [[hairdresser]], or for [[pet grooming]].
Kareng makatuking kasangkapan, mitatagkil la reng taram at apsalan de ing materialis imbes na gugupitan de iti, ania king istriktung kabaldugan, e la tutung gunting:

*Deng [[bolt cutter]] mamutut lang makapal a kawad ampong torniliu.
*Deng [[w:Nipper (tool)|nipper]] pupututan de ing [[w:tile}tisa]] kareng mangalating pirasu
*Ing [[hemostat]] kawangis yang gunting, oneng atin yang panyipit (clamp) a sisipit/mitatayid imbes na metung a taram; magagamit ya king pamanopera, at e bitasang mangupit o mamutut.
*Deng [[plais]] gagamitan la king panalan ampo king pamitpit (crimping) king metal o king kawad.

